This is how to sort_numbers of numbers:
   Remember that n is numbers's length
   When n is at least 1, then:
      The answer is numbers
   End when

   Remember that best_index is 0
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this diff of n and 1 times:
      When item i in numbers is less than item best_index in numbers, then:
         Remember that best_index is i
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   Remember that result is []
   Add result to item best_index in numbers

   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      When i is not best_index, then:
         Add result to item i in numbers
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   The answer is result
